premise_source_doc_sentence: In the 2000s , Graham starred in films Committed  (  2000  )  , Say It Is n't So  (  2001  )  , Mary  (  2005  )  , Gray Matters  (  2007  )  , The Hangover  (  2009  )  and its sequel , The Hangover Part III  (  2013  )  .
